 BLKRAGET failed: Invalid argument
 HDIO_GETGEO failed: Invalid argument
root@lfs:/proc> cat /proc/version 
Linux version 2.4.21-pre6 (root@lfs) (gcc version 3.2.2) #3 Sam Apr 5 20:23:37 CEST 2003
